      "date": "2014-08-27 00:28:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nAre there more debug messages related to changelogs that should move over to D_CHANGELOG?  It looks like there are only five messages in mdc_request.c in total, three of them in changelog_kkuc_cb().\n\nSince this is the second-last debug flag available, it probably makes more sense to just move these few uses over to D_HSM, since that is the primary user of these debug messages.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
